data.description: Welcome to this private, ranch-style home on 9.5 acres with amazing mountain views in La Salle! A wonderful wrap-around deck and pretty stamped concrete front porch provides a warm welcome home and a peaceful place to relax. Through an elegant entryway, find yourself in a completely open floor plan perfect for entertaining or everyday living. The spacious kitchen features modern stainless steel appliances, granite tile countertops, and ample rich wood cabinetry. The living room is sizeable to entertain a group, or relax and take in the views of the plains through the large windows. The generous primary suite provides tons of natural light and a walk-in closet. Additionally, this main level provides 2 more bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a 1/2 bath with space for the washer and dryer. Outside, take in the 360 views from the deck or hot tub. Home upgrades include a sprinkler system and insulation in the shop. Zoned for horses or agricultural use, if desired, and the workshop boasts a swamp cooler and wood-burning stove to escape anytime from the main home. Detached 53'x36' garage/shop and plenty of spaces to park any type of vehicle. Finished for living space, the small connecting silos make a great play space. Home is conveniently located off County Road 49 & County Road 42 with quick access to Hwy 85 and provides less than a 30 minute commute to Greeley, Platteville and other Weld County cities. Don't miss out on making this farmland oasis yours!
